sk.matus.ksp.guitarist_swiss_knife

Class Dependency

  • java.lang.Object
    • sk.matus.ksp.guitarist_swiss_knife.Dependency

  • public class Dependency
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is a representation of a functional dependency. In case all of the terms on the left side of the dependency hold true, the terms on its right side will become true as well
